snippet.title: Johnny Depp Files $50 Million Defamation Lawsuit Against Ex-Wife Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has filed a $50 million defamation lawsuit against ex-wife Amber Heard, claiming her previous domestic abuse allegations are "an elaborate hoax," according to court documents obtained by The Blast. Watch for more details on the former couple's latest legal battle.
